== Tajine l7m ou gombos (le gombo)
mloukhia https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0qTmMZ0Hih8
    tajine agneau gombo
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zdpF2GKjpxM

= Tajine agneau + petits pois + artichaud + cardon
Base : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qiL0gTorp4Q

can also be used with chicken

salt 24h before

600g epaule agneau
    6g salt
        (= 1tsp)
    Maybe use gigot next time
2 gouse d'ail
2 tsp gingembre

1 tsp curcuma
poivre
safran (optional)
2 mini citrons confis
    cut into very small pieces
un peu de persil
to use concentré de tomates ?

200g petits pois : 18g
300g artichauds : 12g carbs
    0.5 tsp salt for these two
    Bring out from freezer beforehand
    artichaud dans eau chaude un peu
    artichaud dans eau + pulco

sauter morceaux tajine sans huile
add 250 ml and deglacer
1h30 feux doux after soft boil
    2 nd position

taste sauce for salt

add petits pois 
add artichauts on top
cook for 20 minutes

remove lid and reduit sauce
add 2 bouchons huile d'olive to the sauce
    and persil


